title: Shocking reason Sinatra isn’t Farrow’s dad
text: Shocking reason Sinatra isn’t Farrow’s dad 0:57 AM New York Post and Network Writers MIA Farrow sensationally hinted Frank Sinatra was the father of her son, Ronan Farrow. But a new book claims that’s impossible. Obama mocks Kanye’s presidential bid 0:15 AM Network Writers and wires KANYE West shocked the world by declaring his run for president in 2020. Now Barack Obama has weighed in on the rapper’s ‘cray’ ambitions. Shatner: Takei is a ‘disturbed individual’ 0:00 AM Jonathon Moran STAR Trek legend William Shatner proves there is still no love lost with ex-castmate George Takei, as he discusses his new role as the face of Foxtel’s latest ad campaign. Princes Wharf 1 stoush deepens 0:00 AM EMMA HOPE THE manager of Princes Wharf 1 has hit back at claims costs to hire the venue are prohibitive, saying a permit restricting the number of events staged there should be lifted.
